#

Red Lentil Borscht

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianvegangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

main

Tags:

souphealthycomfort food

Description

A hearty and vibrant soup that combines the earthy flavors of red lentils with the tanginess of beets, perfect for a nourishing meal.

Ingredients

  • red lentils: 1 cup
  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • carrots: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • potato: 1 medium, diced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
